message.content: Kei te whakapau kaha ahau ki te ētahi whakapā mai i ō whakararuraru. Ka whakapau kaha tātou ki te whakatinana i ēnei raruraru i runga i te whatunga o tōu kamupene. Ka whakararuraru i ēnei whakapā mai me te whakararuraru i ngā pūnaha rorohiko i roto i te whakapā mai o te kamupene. Ka whakararuraru i ēnei raruraru, ka whakauru i ngā whakapā mai ki te whakapā mai i ngā whakapā mai me te whakararuraru i ngā pūnaha rorohiko.
